The_Secret_Lives_of_Dentists http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Secret_Lives_of_Dentists 0 The Secret Lives of Dentists is a 2002 drama film directed by Alan Rudolph. The screenplay was written by Craig Lucas, based on the novella The Age of Grief by Jane Smiley. It was screened at several film festivals, including Sundance and Cannes, and had a limited release in the United States on August 1, 2003.
